remarks.format: ## Remarks 允许活动作者公开具有特定签名的回调，活动的用户可为这些回调提供基于活动的处理程序。The enables activity authors to expose callbacks with specific signatures that users of the activity can provide activity-based handlers for. 是具有返回值的 。 is an that returns a value. 的签名作为泛型类型参数来指定。The signature of the is specified as generic type arguments. 此类型有多个泛型版本，它在参数中采用1到16个，加上 `out` 调用的活动的参数。There are multiple generic versions of this type that take from 1 to 16 in arguments, plus the `out` argument, for the activity that is called. 对于不返回值的活动委托，还有 **ActivityAction** 类型。There are also **ActivityAction** types for activity delegates that do not return values.
